Interface IContainerIPdu

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IIdentifiable, IIPdu, IPdu, IReferrable

    public interface IContainerIPdu
extends IEntity, IIPdu
    IContainerIPdu: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    Allows to collect several IPdus in one ContainerIPdu based on the headerType.
